<topic id="contribute_options_page_from_plugin">
    <title>Contribute a Custom Preferences Page</title>
    <body>
        <p>There is a specific plugin extension type which can be used to contribute a
            <xref
                href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/topics/optionpage-plugin.html"
                format="html" scope="external">custom preferences page</xref>
             to Oxygen's Preferences dialog. An example of how such a page is implemented can be
            found in this sample plugin:
            <xref
                href="https://github.com/oxygenxml/oxygen-dita-prolog-updater/blob/master/src/main/java/com/oxygenxml/prolog/updater/view/PrologOptionPage.java"
                format="java" scope="external"/>
            .</p>
    </body>
